  -files/sshd.rc6.3:
  Removed old files from FILESDIR.

  23 Mar 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> -openssh-5.9_p1-r4.ebuild,
  -openssh-6.0_p1-r1.ebuild, -openssh-6.1_p1-r1.ebuild,
